quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig and the olive
  95,2,And by Mount Sinai
  95,3,And by this city (Makkah) of peace
  95,4,"Surely, We created the human in the best of forms"
  95,5,Then We reverted the human to the lowest of the low
  95,6,"Except for those who believed and did righteous deeds. For them, an unending reward"
  95,7,"What, then, do they deny you [O Prophet] for, post this Judgment [in Verses and above]"
  95,8,Is not Allah the Best of all judges